  "Description": {
    "English": "A large crate of high-capacity vector compressors.<br><br>The creation of interstellar drives often requires dimensions to be condensed and then re-rendered. Such <span class=\"name name-special\">high-tech</span> component manufacture would not be possible without industrial-grade compressors such as these.",
    "SimplifiedChinese": "一大箱高容量向量压缩机。<br><br>制作星际驱动器通常需要将维度压缩后重现。没有这些工业级压缩器的话根本没有办法制造那种<span class=\"name name-special\">高科技</span>构件。",
    "TencentChinese": "一大箱向量压缩器。<br><br>制作星际驱动器通常需要将维度压缩后重现。没有这些工业级压缩器的话根本没有办法制造那种<span class=\"name name-special\">高科技</span>部件。",
    "TraditionalChinese": "一大箱的高容量向量壓縮機。<br><br>製造星際驅動器時常需要將次元壓縮後再重新輸出。唯有使用此類工業用壓縮機才能作出這種<span class=\"name name-special\">高科技</span>元件。"
  },
